  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda wireless stereo hearable \u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0dc4\u0ddc\u0db3 \u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dd4\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Good demand for wireless stereo hearables in India",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A strong demand has been created in the global market for wireless stereo hearables manufactured in India.",
        "The export of these devices has increased by 68 percent. A clear growth has been shown in the quarter since June, where several new devices have been launched in the market.",
        "The low price of Indian devices has thus become a major reason for the increase in their demand.",
        "These devices are sold at a price of 1000 to 2000 Indian rupees."
      ],
